comment._content: I was so delighted, alarmed, amused, and amazed to know there is a place in NSW called "Combanging". So I decided to look it up on GoogleMaps - "Did you mean Combaning?" the Great GoogleGod gasped. Oh well, it might just be worth a look - maps.google.com/maps?f=q&source=s_q&hl=en&geo...
